2006-01-15		Florian Boor <florian.boor@kernelconcepts.de>

	* Release Version 0.6
	* configure.ac, *.am, po/POTFILES.in: Autotools support.
	* gpe-mininet.desktop.in renamed to gpe-mininet.desktop.in.in
	* main.c: Major cleanup and port to use GPE plug instead of libmb.
	          Make use of glib capabilities.
			  Use infoprints instead of tray message.
	* main.c, pixmaps/*48.png: Add additional icons for bigger panels.
	* main.c (clicked): Use gpe function to set menu position.
	
